    <note>Wang(2) Dashou [22102] The medical skill of his father, Keming(2) [22101], apparently gave Dashou access to the imperial leadership--he was appointed to office as Shaoxing Fu Salt official (yanguan) on the basis of a memorial from imperial affinal kinsman, Wu(3) Ju [17706], and was feared and purged by another imperial affinal kinsman, Shi(5) Miyuan [3727]. He was also a disciple of Ye(1) Shi [10749]. Suzhou FZ, 136.10a. CBD, 1, 251.</note>
